# =============================================================================
# API Key Setup Instructions
# =============================================================================

# 1. SERPAPI_API_KEY (Google Search):
#    - Go to https://serpapi.com/dashboard
#    - Sign up for a free account (100 searches/month)
#    - Copy your API key from the dashboard
#    - Set: SERPAPI_API_KEY=your_key_here

# 2. TAVILI_API_KEY (Tavily Research):
#    - Go to https://tavily.com/
#    - Sign up for an account
#    - Get your API key from the dashboard
#    - Set: TAVILI_API_KEY=your_key_here

# 3. NEWSAPI_API_KEY (NewsAPI):
#    - Go to https://newsapi.org/
#    - Sign up for a free account (1000 requests/day)
#    - Copy your API key from the dashboard
#    - Set: NEWSAPI_API_KEY=your_key_here

# =============================================================================
# Environment Variable Setup
# =============================================================================

# Linux/Mac:
# export SERPAPI_API_KEY="your_key_here"
# export TAVILI_API_KEY="your_key_here"
# export NEWSAPI_API_KEY="your_key_here"

# Windows:
# set SERPAPI_API_KEY=your_key_here
# set TAVILI_API_KEY=your_key_here
# set NEWSAPI_API_KEY=your_key_here

# Or add to your .env file:
# SERPAPI_API_KEY=your_key_here
# TAVILI_API_KEY=your_key_here
# NEWSAPI_API_KEY=your_key_here

# =============================================================================
# Troubleshooting
# =============================================================================

# If you get "Engine not available" errors:
# 1. Check that the required API key is set
# 2. Verify the API key is valid (not empty, correct format)
# 3. Check your API quota hasn't been exceeded
# 4. Run get_engine_info() for detailed status

# Common issues:
# - API key not set: Set the environment variable
# - API key invalid: Check the key format and validity
# - Quota exceeded: Check your API usage limits
# - Network issues: Check internet connectivity

# =============================================================================
# Free Tier Limits
# =============================================================================

# SerpAPI: 100 searches/month (free tier)
# Tavily: Check current limits at https://tavily.com/
# NewsAPI: 1000 requests/day (free tier)

# For production use, consider upgrading to paid plans for higher limits.